# # n6-architecture/.own.cognitive (mk2)
#
# Schema authority: hive/spec/schema/own_v1.schema.yaml
# Format: mk2 frontmatter (#-prefixed YAML) + raw-format body (`own N <status> "name"` blocks).
# raw_loader.hexa silently skips `#`-prefixed lines so the body parses unchanged.
# Authoritative rule content lives in `own N <status> ...` blocks below.
#
# ## scope
# Cross-domain cognitive / design / framing rules. Sister files (mk2 split):
# - .own.readme   — README.md governance (own#14 / own#17 / own#20 / own#21 / own#29)
# - .own.group_p  — papers/*.md governance (own#6, mk2 unified collapsing precedent)
# - .own.cognitive — THIS file: framing rules spanning domains/** + theory/** +
#                    Atlas constants registry + axis / slot / enumeration design surfaces
#
# ## roles
# - dancinlife (project owner)
# - claude opus / sonnet / haiku (AI agents — autonomous within own baselines)
#
# ## baselines
# - own 32 n6-no-fixation-design-and-count — design constants force-fit ban + enumeration
#   count-cap fixation ban 통합 (mk2 unified, 2026-05-07; mk1 own#32 promoted 2026-05-01)
#
# ## predecessor_lineage
# - mk1 .own (881L, 35 rules, retired 2026-05-03 commit 442afa7b)
# - mk1 own#32 physical-limit-alternative-framing (2026-05-01) — design-constant scope
#   원본; mk2 reconstruction 시 본 파일에서 enumeration count-cap scope 흡수하여
#   unified rule 로 합병 (hive raw.mk2 arch.001 / .own.group_p own#6 collapsing 패턴
#   미러링).
# - mk2 unified absorbs:
#   - mk1 own#32 (design constants force-fit ban; HARD-OPT-IN)
#   - 2026-05-07 사용자 directive "n=6 집착금지 / 6개를 한계로 두는 케이스가 너무 많아
#     / 더 나은게 발견될 수 있는데" (enumeration count-cap fixation ban; advisory)
#
# ## cross_link_to_raws
# - raw 0 (root-ssot) — .raw + .own + .guide triad
# - raw 91 (honest-c3-disclosure) — process-quality + honest C1-C5
# - raw 95 (triad-mandate) — hive-agent + cli-lint + advisory tri-layer
